{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Div.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.div\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnpackedFloat</span>.<span class=\"name\">div</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">spec</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.Format\">Format</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Basic.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat\">UnpackedFloat</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Basic.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat\">UnpackedFloat</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Basic.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat\">UnpackedFloat</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Computes the quotient of two floating point numbers and rounds the result according to\nthe given specification.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Div.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.div","kind":"def","line":42,"name":"Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.div","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Div.lean#L42-L59"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Div.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.divCore\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnpackedFloat</span>.<span class=\"name\">divCore</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">spec</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.Format\">Format</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"de